<plot>An overview of an academic conference commemorating the 50th anniversary of the destruction of the Vilna Ghetto held in Vilna in 1993, this film opens with an overview of the history of Lithuania and the Jews of Lithuania. The production includes contemporary footage juxtaposed with historical film and photographs of the once vibrant Jewish community of Vilna.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?130791</url></doc>
